description: ['The Danby Designer line of compact refrigerators is dedicated to being well built, easily maintained and convenient. The DAR026A1BDD-6 model comes in at a height of just over two feet and features 2.6 cu. ft. (73 L) of cooling capacity. Quality can look good, with its sleek exterior, this is the ideal unit for floors and countertops, making it the perfect fridge for spaces such as dormitory rooms, wet bars, rec-rooms, dens, workshops and basement lounges. Integrated door shelving with tall bottle storage makes storing all your additional drinks and snacks easy. Accessories can be stored on the scratch-resistant worktop and there’s no need to defrost the unit as it’s done automatically. This appliance also comes with a mechanical thermostat and offers 2.5 strong wire shelves for maximum storage versatility and optimal cool air circulation. Both left and right-handed users will love the convenient reversible door swing and the integrated door handle. This mini fridge is designed to blend with any decor style seamlessly.']

title: Kenmore 99091 Compact Refrigerator, Red
features: ['COMPACT MINI FRIDGE : Mini refrigerator and freezer has a total capacity of 4.4 cubic feet, and features a retro design to add vintage style to dorm rooms, offices, and garages', 'KEEP FOOD AND DRINKS COLD: With the mechanical temperature control, refrigerated food and beverages will be consistently kept cold and fresh', "CRISP, FRESH FOOD: Keep fruits and vegetables fresh with the clear crisper drawer, and allows quick access to your food items and makes it easy to spot what you're looking for", 'CHILLS QUICKLY: Separate cooling compartment is lower in temperature than the rest of the mini fridge, allowing you to cool items in a shorter time period', 'COMPACT FRIDGE DIMENSIONS: 19.3" W x 22.8" D x 36.1" H']
description: ['With the Kenmore 4.4 Cubic Feet Retro Compact Mini Fridge, you’ll be able to store excess food and drinks easily. The small refrigerator is portable and can be used at work under your desk, in the garage, or off at college in a dorm room. The retro mini fridge will add trendy vintage style to any room or living space. The thermostat lets you control the temperature with a simple turn of the knob. You’ll never have to worry about cold storage foods and drinks going bad. A separate chilling compartment gets items chilled in a hurry. Convenience features include adjustable glass shelves that can be removed to create customizable food storage and accommodate tall items and are also easy to clean. features: ['1-2/3-cubic-foot refrigerator/freezer with recessed, space-saving door handle', 'Rotary temperature-control dial; 7 temperature settings; manual defrost', 'Full-width slide-out wire shelf; full-width and half-width door-storage shelf', '2-liter bottle storage; half-width freezer compartment; ice-cube tray included', 'Measures approximately 18-3/5 by 17-1/2 by 19-3/5 inches']
description: ["Equally useful in a college student's dorm room as it is in a home or away office, this compact, freestanding refrigerator/freezer unit makes it possible to keep meals, snacks, and beverages properly chilled for later enjoyment. The unit's 1-2/3-cubic-foot interior offers a handy layout for keeping items neatly organized. It comes with a full-width slide-out wire shelf, a full-width and half-width door-storage shelf, 2-liter bottle storage, and a half-width freezer compartment with an ice-cube tray. The unit's rotary temperature-control dial mounted on the back makes it possible to turn the unit off or adjust the thermostat as desired. Choose from seven temperature settings; the appliance automatically maintains the temperature level selected. Other highlights include a recessed door handle, a drip tray, manual defrost, and a coil back that works as a condenser to release heat trapped inside the refrigerator. The UL-approved refrigerator/freezer weighs a little over 38 pounds and measures approximately 18-3/5 by 17-1/2 by 19-3/5 inches."]

title: Danby Contemporary Classic DAR017A3BDB-6 1.7 Cu.Ft. Mini Fridge, Countertop Compact Refrigerator for Bedroom, Office, Desk-E-Star Rated, in Matte Black
features: ['Compact Countertop Mini Fridge: This Danby Contemporary Classic Mini Fridge is the perfect size to fit countertops or desktops and is an ideal mini fridge for your bedroom, office, or dorm', '1.7 Cubic Feet (49 Liters) Capacity: The All refrigerator unit is small but mighty with 1.7 cu. ft. of fridge space', 'Integrated Door Shelving: Tall bottle storage is ideal for large pop, water, juice, or other drink bottles', 'CanStor Beverage Dispensing System: Efficient and tidy can storage integrated into the mini refrigerator door', 'Clean, Bright and Modern: White interior with bright LED lighting, glass shelves, rubber-grip ergonomic door handle, and matte black door finish provide an enhanced clean look', 'Fits anywhere: Smooth back design with no bulky exposed components means this small mini fridge can fit just about anywhere in your room', 'Versatile: Reversible hidden door hinges, functional textured scratch resistant worktop and adjustable shelving', 'Easy to Operate: Automatic defrost means no extra maintenance on your part', 'Environmentally Friendly: Energy Star compliant and uses environmental-friendly R600a refrigerant']
description: ['Drawing inspiration from mid-century styling and simplicity, Danby’s patented Contemporary Classic collection of compact refrigerators reimagine retro for the modern consumer. Featuring Danby’s exclusive retro-inspired curved door design, matte black door finish, rubber-grip ergonomic handle and stylized worktop, its exterior features are only outmatched by its signature interior. Boasting 1. 7 cubic-feet (49 liters) of storage and cooling space, it features one and a half tempered glass shelves for maximum storage versatility. There’s more than enough room for larger bottles and the spacious unit helps keep electricity bills in check with its Energy Star rating and state-of-the-art mechanical thermostat. Maintenance and cleaning are as simple as can be with the automatic defrost system. It also includes an efficient CanStor beverage dispenser and reliable interior white LED light. This model is built for convenience as the reversible door hinge allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening.']

title: Whirlpool 33 in. W 20.5 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in White
description: ["There's always a place for fresh and frozen favorites inside this 33 in. wide 20.5 cu. ft. Whirlpool top-freezer refrigerator. Enjoy a steady supply of ice conveniently with the addition of the optional (sold separately) ice maker Upfront temperature control makes temperature management easy, by placing the interior controls at the front of the refrigerator 2 Clear, humidity controlled crispers help keep fruits and vegetables fresh and organized Adjustable gallon-size on-door storage is ideal for frequently accessed items and large containers 14.42 cu. ft. fresh food compartment and 6.08 cu. ft. freezer compartment Freezer door shelves and a full-width wire freezer compartment shelf help keep your freezer organized Flexi-Slide deli drawer easily moves from one side to the refrigerator to the other for convenient storage options Flexible installation with reversible doors. Ships with as a right-hand door swing. title: Haier HNSB02SS 1-2/3-Cubic-Foot Freestanding Refrigerator/Freezer, Stainless Steel
features: ['1-2/3-cubic-foot refrigerator/freezer with recessed, space-saving door handle', 'Rotary temperature-control dial; 7 temperature settings; manual defrost', 'Full-width slide-out wire shelf; full-width and half-width door-storage shelf', '2-liter bottle storage; half-width freezer compartment; ice-cube tray included', 'Measures approximately 18-3/5 by 17-1/2 by 19-3/5 inches']
description: ["Equally useful in a college student's dorm room as it is in a home or away office, this compact, freestanding refrigerator/freezer unit makes it possible to keep meals, snacks, and beverages properly chilled for later enjoyment. The unit's 1-2/3-cubic-foot interior offers a handy layout for keeping items neatly organized. It comes with a full-width slide-out wire shelf, a full-width and half-width door-storage shelf, 2-liter bottle storage, and a half-width freezer compartment with an ice-cube tray. The unit's rotary temperature-control dial mounted on the back makes it possible to turn the unit off or adjust the thermostat as desired. Choose from seven temperature settings; the appliance automatically maintains the temperature level selected. Other highlights include a recessed door handle, a drip tray, manual defrost, and a coil back that works as a condenser to release heat trapped inside the refrigerator. Attractively housed in stainless steel, the UL-approved refrigerator/freezer weighs a little over 38 pounds and measures approximately 18-3/5 by 17-1/2 by 19-3/5 inches."]

title: Haier HNSE05BB 4-3/5-Cubic-Foot Compact Refrigerator/Freezer, Black/Stainless
features: ['4-3/5-cubic-foot compressor-cooled refrigerator/freezer with rotary thermostat', 'Half-width freezer compartment; handy ice-cube tray; manual defrost', '3 adjustable full-width glass shelves; full-width convertible drip/storage tray', '3 door shelves fit 2-liter and gallon-size containers; Dispense-a-Can storage space', 'Measures approximately 22-1/4 by 20-1/2 by 32 inches; 1-year limited warranty']
description: ["Small enough for a college dorm room, a studio apartment, or an office or workshop, this compact, freestanding refrigerator/freezer, with its 4-3/5-cubic-foot capacity, makes it easy to keep food and beverages properly chilled and neatly organized. The unit's half-width freezer compartment includes a handy ice-cube tray, while its refrigerator space provides three, adjustable, full-width glass shelves for storing fresh food. The refrigerator also supplies a full-width convertible drip/storage tray and three door shelves (two full-width and one half-width) that accommodate 2-liter bottles, gallon-size jugs, containers of yogurt, and more. For added convenience, its Dispense-a-Can storage space keeps a variety of favorite beverages easily accessible. Other details include manual defrost with a defrost drain, a rotary thermostat, adjustable leveling legs to balance the appliance if it sits on uneven ground, and a reversible door (can be hinged to open from the left or right side) with a recessed handle for a sleek look. Compressor cooled with a space-saving flat-back design, the compact refrigerator/freezer measures approximately 22-1/4 by 20-1/2 by 32 inches and carries a one-year limited warranty."]

description: ['"Take your backyard barbeques to the next level, with the addition of a Danby outdoor refrigerator. This unit is made for durability in exterior conditions with its 4 rust-resistant castors for easy portability, waterproof electrical housing and water resistant coating. Be BBQ ready with its 4. 4 cubic-feet (124 liters) of storage and cooling space. This mini fridge features two glass shelves for maximum storage versatility as well as another half shelf for additional snacks, sauces or drinks. Add in an additional clear vegetable crisper with glass top for all those fresh summer fruits and vegetables. This mini fridge feature’s Danby’s exclusive Contemporary Classic retro-inspired curved door design, rubber-grip ergonomic handle and stylized worktop, perfect for serving up snacks. It also comes with an efficient CanStor beverage dispenser and bright LED interior lights. As always, this mini fridge has a reversible door hinge, allowing you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. Bring a Danby to your next outdoor party and experience the convenience from a brand you trust.']

features: ['4.4 cu. ft. (126 L) capacity compact all fridge.', 'Energy Star compliant. Environmentally friendly R600a refrigerant. Reversible door hinge.', 'Spotless steel door finish - looks identical to real stainless steel but without the smudging. Scratch resistant worktop.']
description: ['Product Description', 'This elegant compact refrigerator by Danby can easily fulfill your family’s needs with its 4.4 cubic-feet (126 litres) of storage and cooling space. It features two full shelves for maximum storage versatility as well as another half shelf for additional items and a see-through vegetable crisper with glass top. There’s more than enough room for larger bottles and the spacious unit helps keep electricity bills in check with its Energy Star rating and state-of-the-art mechanical thermostat. Maintenance and cleaning are as simple as can be with the automatic defrost system and spotless-steel finish. The spotless-steel door, black cabinet, and integrated door handle provide a beautiful contemporary look and the smart scratch-resistant work-top is an ideal place to store accessories. It also comes with an efficient CanStor beverage dispenser and reliable interior light. This model is built for convenience as the reversible door hinge allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening.', 'From the Manufacturer', 'This elegant compact refrigerator by Danby can easily fulfill your family’s needs with its 4.4 cubic-feet of storage and cooling space. It features two full shelves for maximum storage versatility as well as another half shelf for additional items and a see-through vegetable crisper with glass top. There’s more than enough room for larger bottles and the spacious unit helps keep electricity bills in check with its Energy Star rating and state-of-the-art mechanical thermostat. In addition, environmentally friendly R600a coolant is the refrigerant used in this unit. Maintenance and cleaning are as simple as can be with the automatic defrost system and spotless-steel finish. The spotless-steel door, black cabinet, and integrated door handle provide a beautiful contemporary look and the smart scratch-resistant work-top is an ideal place to store accessories. It also comes with an efficient CanStor beverage dispenser and reliable interior light. This model is built for convenience as the reversible door hinge allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This esteemed refrigerator also comes with a worry-free 18-month warranty on parts and labour with handy in-home service.']

features: ['4-3/5-cubic-foot freestanding refrigerator/freezer with 3 adjustable glass shelves', 'Full-width storage/drip tray; half-width freezer compartment with ice-cube tray', 'Door storage includes 2 shelves, tall-bottle shelf, and dispense-a-can storage bin', 'Rotary thermostat; manual defrost; adjustable leveling legs for balance; flat-back design', 'Measures 22-1/4 by 20-5/16 by 32-1/16 inches; 1-year limited warranty']
description: ['With its 4-3/5-cubic-foot capacity, this compact-size refrigerator/freezer works great for a bar area or dorm room, or during the holidays when extra space comes in handy. The refrigerator provides three, full-width, adjustable, glass shelves; a full-width convertible storage/drip tray; and a half-width freezer compartment with an ice-cube tray. Its door features two full-width storage shelves, one half-width shelf that accommodates tall bottles, and a dispense-a-can storage bin that make great use of space and provide easy access to ice-cold beer and soda. Even more, its reversible door can be attached to open from either the left or the right side, while adjustable leveling legs allow for balancing the unit if it sits on uneven ground. Other highlights include a rotary thermostat, manual defrost, a recessed handle, a defrost drain, and a space-saving flat-back design. The freestanding refrigerator/freezer measures 22-1/4 by 20-5/16 by 32-1/16 inches and carries a one-year limited parts-and-labor warranty with a five-year limited warranty on the sealed system.']

description: ['Product Description', "Forget running to the kitchen, enjoy the convenience of chilled beverages where they're needed most with our Energy Star rated Danby Designer compact all fridge. Boasting a generous capacity of 4.4 cu. ft. this counter high model is an efficient way to supplement your refrigerator. It includes our Canstor beverage dispenser, reversible door hinge and interior light.", 'From the Manufacturer', 'There’s no need to wear out a path to the kitchen every time you’re in the mood for a refreshing drink or snack. This compact, counter-high fridge by Danby is the ideal solution since it’s a perfect fit for any room in your home. It boasts a generous 4.4 cubic feet of cooling capacity and is outfitted with the popular CanStor beverage dispenser. Your electricity costs will be reduced due to the Energy-Star rating and highly-efficient mechanical thermostat. It uses R600a refrigerant to cool the interior. The white finish is easy to clean since it won’t smudge and the cycle defrosting system keeps it from freezing up. This spacious model offers two-and-a-half slide-out wire shelves along with a full-width door shelf and a pair of three-quarter-width door shelves for maximum storage room. There’s an attractive and functional clear vegetable crisper and cover inside along with a bright interior light for easy viewing. The integrated door handle ensures easy opening and the reversible door swing means it can be adjusted for either left or right-handed use. This stunning appliance also comes with 18-months coverage on parts and labor.']

title: Summit SPR627OS Outdoor Built-In Undercounter All-Refrigerator with Glass Shelves and Lock, 24", Stainless Steel/Black
features: ['Durable design built to last in outdoor kitchens', 'Designed for built-in undercounter installation in 24” wide settings', 'Stainless steel door includes keyed lock and pro handle', 'Deluxe interior with LED lighting, glass shelves, and a digital thermostat', 'Commercial grade design that meets NSF standards']
description: ['Summit Appliance offers a quality line of built-in all-refrigerators specially designed for user-friendly operation in outdoor settings. Model SPR627OS is a 24” wide all-refrigerator that can be used built-in or freestanding in any outdoor location. It comes with a jet black cabinet and a user-reversible stainless steel door equipped with a pro style handle and front lock. The sealed back design and ground fault circuit interrupter offer added safety from the elements in the outdoors. Frost-free operation ensures minimum maintenance, with digital controls for easy temperature management. Adjustable glass shelves offer easy storage, with a slotted floor that can safely hold bottles in place. Additional features include LED lighting and a Sabbath mode setting. The flat door liner is great for fitting deeper trays inside. The SPR627OS can be used in household or commercial settings. It is ETL-S listed to NSF-7 commercial standards and ENERGY STAR® certified as a commercial refrigerator.']

description: ['Product Description', 'Danby’s large capacity, counter-high fridge offers plenty of additional refrigeration in a compact space. Suitable for rec-rooms, dens and workshops this 4.4 cu. ft. model includes our patented Canstor beverage dispenser, full width freezer section and tall bottle storage.', 'From the Manufacturer', 'When you’re in need of a counter-high refrigerator that offers a large storage area in a compact space there’s no need to look any further than Danby’s DCR044A2WDD model. This high-tech unit offers 4.4 cubic feet of refrigeration capacity and is ideal for workshops, dens, rec-rooms and lunchrooms etc. It’s outfitted with a convenient CanStor beverage dispenser for your favorite drinks and has more than enough room for tall bottles. The 2.5 glass shelf design offers maximum storage versatility and the appliance is controlled by an accurate mechanical thermostat and simple push-button defrosting system. If you need to freeze certain types of foods or are simply looking for a place to make and store ice cubes this appliance meets the requirements as it also features a full- width independent freezer section. Since this attractive model is also Energy Star rated it won’t raise your power bills. It also uses Eco-friendly, natural R600a refrigerant to help our environment. This classy compact fridge comes in an appealing white finish, making it suitable for any style of existing décor. It also comes with an integrated door handle with a convenient reversible door hinge for both left and right-handed opening. The smooth back design enables the fridge to be placed flush against a wall and it comes with a generous 18-month warranty on parts and labor with in-home service.']

title: Haier ESR042PBB 4.1-Cu-Ft Compact Refrigerator/Freezer, Black
features: ['4.1-cubic-foot refrigerator with full-width freezer compartment', '2 full-width shelves; full-width clear crisper drawer; door storage', 'Dual "dispense-a-can" drink-storage bins; reversible door; manual defrost', 'Adjustable leveling legs; lock and key for security; adjustable thermostat', 'Measures 21-5/8 by 19-9/16 by 34 inches; 1-year parts-and-labor warranty']
description: ['With its 4.09-cubic-foot capacity, this compact-size refrigerator/freezer works great for a bar area or dorm room, or during the holidays when extra space can come in handy. The unit provides two full-width shelves (one fixed and one adjustable), a full-width clear crisper drawer with a glass cover, and a full-width freezer compartment with an ice-cube tray. Its door features a full-width storage shelf, 2-liter bottle storage, and dual "dispense-a-can" drink-storage bins that make great use of space and provide easy access to ice-cold soda, beer, and juice. Even more, its reversible door can be set up to open from either the left or the right side, while adjustable legs allow for stabilizing the unit if it sits on an uneven surface. Other highlights include a security lock and key, an adjustable thermostat, manual defrost, a drip tray, and an Energy Star rating for efficiency. The freestanding refrigerator/freezer measures 21-5/8 by 19-9/16 by 34 inches and carries a one-year parts-and-labor warranty with a five-year warranty on the compressor.']

title: Danby Designer 2.6 cu. ft. Compact Refrigerator (DAR026A1WDD), White
features: ['2.6 cu. ft. (73 L) capacity compact all refrigerator', 'Energy Star compliant. Environmentally friendly R600a refrigerant. Automatic defrost system.', '2 full width and 1 - 1/2 width adjustable wire shelves. Tall bottle storage - great for large soda bottles. CanStor beverage dispensing system.', 'Mechanical thermostat.', 'Scratch resistant worktop.']
description: ['Product Description', 'You can add a touch of class to any room in your home or office with this striking compact refrigerator by Danby. It comes in at a height of just over two feet and features 2.6 cu. ft. (73 L) of cooling capacity. It’s the ideal unit for floors and countertops, making it the perfect fridge for spaces such as dormitory rooms and wet bars. Finding storage room for tall bottles is no problem at all and the third-generation CanStor beverage dispenser is second to none. Accessories can easily be stored on the scratch-resistant worktop and there’s no need to defrost the unit as it’s done automatically. This splendid appliance also comes with a mechanical thermostat and offers 2.5 strong wire shelves for maximum storage versatility. Both left and right-handed users will love the convenient reversible door swing and the integrated door handle.', 'From the Manufacturer', 'You can add a touch of class to any room in your home or office with this striking compact all refrigerator by Danby. It comes in at a height of just over two feet and features 2.6 cubic feet of cooling capacity. It’s the ideal unit for floors and countertops, making it the perfect fridge for spaces such as dormitory rooms and wet bars. This unit is Energy Star rated and used Eco-friendly, natural R600a refrigerant. Finding storage room for tall bottles is no problem at all and the third-generation CanStor beverage dispenser is second to none. Accessories can easily be stored on the scratch-resistant worktop and there’s no need to defrost the unit as it’s done automatically. This splendid appliance also comes with a mechanical thermostat and offers 2.5 strong wire shelves for maximum storage versatility. Both left and right-handed users will love the convenient reversible door swing and the integrated door handle. This compact unit also comes with a parts and labor warranty of 18 months.']

features: ['Compact Mini Fridge: This Danby compact refrigerator with freezer is the ideal mini fridge for apartments, basements, family rooms, dorms, offices, or the cottage', '4.7 Cubic Feet (133 Liters) Capacity Mini Fridge: The refrigerator unit is roomy with 4.57 cu. ft. of fridge space', '1.5 Cubic Feet (42 Liters) Freezer: Sperate freezer takes this mini fridge to the next level', 'Integrated Door Shelving: Tall bottle storage is ideal for large pop, water, juice, or other drink bottles', 'Clean Bright and Modern: White interior, 2 full width adjustable glass shelves, fresh vegetable crisper with glass cover and integrated door handle', 'Fits anywhere: Reversible door hinge means this mini fridge can fit just about anywhere in your room', 'Versatile: Fresh vegetable crisper, and true freezer section is perfect for those looking for a mini fridge with freezer', 'Easy to Operate: Mechanical thermostat and handy manual defrost', 'Environmentally Friendly: Energy Star compliant and uses environmental-friendly R600a refrigerant']
description: ['Having separate fridge and freezer refrigerators is definitely a great thing! You get that convenient combination and much more with this splendid dual-door compact refrigerator by Danby. This model offers 4.7 cu. ft. of cooling and freezing capacity and is Energy-Star compliant to help keep electricity costs as low as possible. The popular appliance is a perfect match for apartments, rec-rooms, bars, cottages and offices. It has a high-tech mechanical thermostat to make sure your foods are always stored at the correct temperature and has a handy cycle defrosting system. It comes with an intelligent reversible-door feature which allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This glamorous fridge/freezer is a breeze to keep clean due to the stunning Black Stainless finish. Inside the appliance you’ll find a bright interior light as well as a see-through vegetable crisper with glass cover and plenty of space for tall bottles. The integrated door handle adds another touch of class. This highly-efficient appliance also features an 12 month warranty on parts and labor.']

title: Haier HSA04WNCWW Compact 3-8/9-Cu-Ft Refrigerator/Freezer, White
features: ['Stylish compact refrigerator/freezer with 3-8/9-cubic-foot capacity', '3 full-width slide-out wire shelves; 3 full-width door-storage shelves', '2-liter bottle storage; full-width freezer compartment with ice-cube tray', 'Adjustable thermostat; manual defrost; drip tray; leveling legs for stability', 'Measures 19-1/8 by 18-3/4 by 33-7/8 inches; 1-year parts-and-labor warranty']
description: ["With its 3-8/9-cubic-foot capacity, this stylish compact refrigerator/freezer can be used in any home, dorm room, or office, working great as a backup fridge for snacks and beverages or for extra food during the holidays. It comes equipped with three full-width slide-out wire shelves, three full-width door-storage shelves, 2-liter bottle storage, and a full-width freezer compartment with an ice-cube tray. The unit's adjustable thermostat can be controlled by the rotary temperature-control dial, while its manual-defrost function helps save on energy costs. Thoughtfully designed, the appliance features a recessed door handle, making the unit flat and space saving in the front, and a coil back that works as a condensor to release heat trapped inside the refrigerator. It also provides a quick-cleaning drip tray and two front leveling legs that can be made longer or shorter to balance the unit if it sits on uneven ground. The refrigerator/freezer measures 19-1/8 by 18-3/4 by 33-7/8 inches and carries a one-year parts-and-labor warranty with a five-year warranty on the compressor."]

features: ['4.4 cu. ft. (124 L) capacity compact all fridge.', 'Energy Star compliant. Environmentally friendly R600a refrigerant. description: ['Product Description', "Forget running to the kitchen, enjoy the convenience of chilled beverages where they're needed most with our Energy Star rated Danby Designer compact all fridge. Boasting a generous capacity of 4.4 cu. ft. this counter high model is an efficient way to supplement your refrigerator. It includes our Canstor beverage dispenser, reversible door hinge and interior light.", 'From the Manufacturer', 'There’s no need to wear out a path to the kitchen every time you’re in the mood for a refreshing drink or snack. This compact, counter-high fridge by Danby is the ideal solution since it’s a perfect fit for any room in your home. It boasts a generous 4.4 cubic feet of cooling capacity and is outfitted with the popular CanStor beverage dispenser. Your electricity costs will be reduced due to the Energy-Star rating and highly-efficient mechanical thermostat. It uses environmentally friendly R600a refrigerant to cool the interior. The black finish is easy to clean since it won’t smudge and the cycle defrosting system keeps it from freezing up. This spacious model offers two-and-a-half slide-out glass shelves along with a full-width door shelf and a pair of three-quarter-width door shelves for maximum storage room. There’s an attractive and functional clear vegetable crisper and cover inside along with a bright interior light for easy viewing. The integrated door handle ensures easy opening and the reversible door swing means it can be adjusted for either left or right-handed use. This stunning appliance also comes with 18-months coverage on parts and labor.']

This high-tech unit offers 4.4 cubic feet (126 L) of refrigeration capacity and is ideal for workshops, dens, rec-rooms and lunchrooms etc. It’s outfitted with a convenient CanStor beverage dispenser for your favourite drinks and has more than enough room for tall bottles. The 2.5-shelf design offers maximum storage versatility and the appliance is controlled by an accurate mechanical thermostat and simple semi-automatic defrosting system. If you need to freeze certain types of foods or are simply looking for a place to make and store ice cubes this appliance meets the requirements as it also features a full- width independent freezer section. Since this attractive model is also Energy Star rated it won’t raise your power bills. This classy compact fridge can be found in white, black and smudge-free spotless steel finishes, making it suitable for any style of existing décor. In addition, it comes with an integrated door handle with a convenient reversible door hinge for both left and right-handed opening.', 'From the Manufacturer', 'When you’re in need of a counter-high refrigerator that offers a large storage area in a compact space there’s no need to look any further than Danby’s DCR044A2BDD model. description: ['Over 5 cu.ft. of storage capacity in a perfectly sized 24" footprint. Includes adjustable glass shelves for spill-proof storage. Improved temperature performance with our unique dual evaporator cooling. Zero degree freezer compartment. Door racks provide convenient storage options. Made in Europe. Dimensions: 33.25" H x 23.63" W x 23.5" D. AAccuCold by Summit Appliance offers a wide range of counter height refrigeration for general purpose storage. The CT66J Series includes freestanding refrigerator-freezers equipped with dual evaporator cooling for optimum storage conditions. Sized with a 24" footprint, the CT66B offers over 5 cu.ft. of storage capacity. This counter height model is designed for freestanding use. It features a black exterior finish and a user-reversible door swing. Inside, our unique dual evaporator system separately cools the refrigerator and freezer section to ensure proper storage temperature. Cycle defrost operation reduces user maintenance in the automatic defrost fresh food section, while the manual defrost freezer compartment can maintain zero degrees. Door storage provides easy access for tall bottles and small condiments. Additional features include adjustable shelves, a clear crisper, and automatic interior lighting. The CT66B has long proven itself to have one of the best temperature performance records in the industry. To see additional finish options on this unit, browse the full CT66 Series. For built-in undercounter applications, see the CT66BBI. NOTE: This unit is designed for general purpose, medical, or commercial applications and does not meet DOE energy standards for residential use. FOR MEDICAL USE ONLY.']

description: ["With its 2-2/3-cubic-foot capacity, this compact refrigerator/freezer keeps food fresh and beverages ice cold. It works great in an office or dorm room, or as a back-up fridge around the holidays when extra space comes in handy. Thoughtfully designed, the appliance features a recessed door handle, making the unit flat and space saving in the front, and a coil back that works as a condenser to release heat trapped inside the refrigerator. It also provides a quick-cleaning drip tray and two front leveling legs that can be made longer or shorter to balance the unit if it sits on uneven ground. The refrigerator/freezer measures 19-1/8 by 18-3/4 by 26-1/8 inches and carries a one-year parts-and-labor warranty with a five-year warranty on the compressor."]

features: ['Compact refrigerator/freezer with 2-2/3-cubic-foot capacity', '2 full-width slide-out wire shelves; 2 full-width door-storage shelves', '2-liter bottle storage; half-width freezer compartment with ice-cube tray', 'Adjustable thermostat; manual defrost; drip tray; leveling legs for stability', 'Measures 19-1/8 by 18-3/4 by 26-1/8 inches; 1-year parts-and-labor warranty']
description: ["With its 2-2/3-cubic-foot capacity, this compact refrigerator/freezer keeps food fresh and beverages ice cold. It works great in an office or dorm room, or as a back-up fridge around the holidays when extra space comes in handy. The unit provides two full-width slide-out wire shelves, two full-width door-storage shelves, 2-liter bottle storage, and a half-width freezer compartment with an ice-cube tray. The unit's adjustable thermostat can be controlled by the rotary temperature-control dial, while its manual-defrost function helps save on energy costs. Thoughtfully designed, the appliance features a recessed door handle, making the unit flat and space saving in the front, and a coil back that works as a condensor to release heat trapped inside the refrigerator. It also provides a quick-cleaning drip tray and two front leveling legs that can be made longer or shorter to balance the unit if it sits on uneven ground. The refrigerator/freezer measures 19-1/8 by 18-3/4 by 26-1/8 inches and carries a one-year parts-and-labor warranty with a five-year warranty on the compressor."]

title: Kenmore 33" Top-Freezer Refrigerator with 21 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, Stainless Steel
features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 21 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with door storage provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Full-width shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'LED LIGHTING: Long-lasting LED lights provide warm, natural lighting to help you find what you need quickly and take stock of what you need on your next trip to the grocery store', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 32 7/8" W x 33.8" D x 67.25" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 21 cubic ft. of interior space and energy efficient LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features full-width shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The 2 clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh. With the refrigerator\'s door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The fridge can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a stainless steel finish measures 32 7/8" W x 33.8" D x 67.25" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

features: ['Item includes room of choice delivery, unboxing, item hook-up and free optional haul-away at checkout', 'This Kenmore Elite 2-Door Bottom Freezer fridge has an ample 24.1 cu. ft. of space so you can comfortably fit in household staples, snacks and party trays', 'The full-width pantry drawer is the perfect spot to stash snacks, treats, deli trays and more without crowding up the rest of the fridge.Depth w/ Handle (inches) : 34.875. Depth w/o Handle (inches) : 33. Depth w/ Door Open 90 Degrees : 62.75. Width w/ Door Closed (Inches) : 32.75. Depth without Door (inches) :29', 'The 2 AirTight Crisper drawers give your produce an optimal environment, so carrots stay crisp and apples stay sweet', 'Multi Air Flow Technology ensures that temperatures stay nice and even throughout the fridge and the freezer stays frost-free', 'The Kenmore Tilt-N-Store door bin flips up and out of the way to create more vertical space to store taller items like wine bottles and pitchers with ease']
description: ['The Kenmore Elite 79042 24.1 cu. ft. 2-Door Bottom-Freezer Fridge was designed to give you plenty of versatile storage space and to keep your foods fresher, longer. Stash snacks, tasty treats and delicious leftovers alongside fresh produce and household staples without worrying about keeping the fridge organized. A full-width pantry drawer is perfect for pies, pizzas and party trays while the adjustable glass shelves let you customize how you use the interior capacity of the fridge. Adjustable shelving door storage gives you plenty of food storage flexibility, even if you come home with way more groceries than you anticipated. Gallon storage bins and a Tilt-N-Store door bin accommodate wide and tall items with ease. No more puzzling out how to fit in milk, wine or juice next to the salad dressing and soda. Multi Air Flow technology works to keep cool fresh air flowing throughout the fridge while the humidity-controlled crisper drawers keep produce crisp and bright. Kenmore’s Multi Air Flow technology uses venting to help balance cool air throughout the whole fridge, even the door space. 2 humidity-controlled crisper drawers keep delicate produce fresher longer. No more wasting food. Keep pre-made meals at-the-ready and treats close at hand in this 2-tier pull-out bottom freezer. No more digging through piles of peas for a Friday night pizza. A built-in icemaker in the bottom freezer keeps fresh ice at your fingertips. Just reach in and grab a handful, whether you’re hosting cocktail hour or whipping up iced coffee for brunch. Keep more fresh food at your fingertips in this Kenmore Elite bottom freezer fridge.']

title: Kenmore Top-Freezer Refrigerator with LED Lighting and 20.8 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, White
features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 20.8 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with two crisper drawers provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Features slide-out glass storage shelves for easy access and removal of pies, cakes, casseroles, and larger food items, as well as LED lighting for a warm, natural light', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Adjustable, easy to remove shelving customizes your storage space, while gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items', 'LOW MAINTENANCE, HIGH PERFORMANCE: Clean back design hides condenser coils, preventing the accumulation of dust and providing you with better refrigerating performance and less maintenance', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 33.8" x 32.87" x 66.1" for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space in your home, office, or garage']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 20.8 cubic ft. of interior space and long-lasting LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features full-width adjustable glass shelves to suit your food storage needs and 2 clear plastic crisper drawers to keep fruits and vegetables fresh. It also features slide-out glass storage shelves for easy access and removal of pies, cakes, casseroles, and larger food items. With the refrigerator\'s convenient door storage, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The gallon door bins make it easy to store tall items and beverages alongside your favorite sauces, condiments, and other ingredients. The tall item accommodation on the bottom shelf means more space for bottles of wine and water. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized with two door bins and a single shelf. It also helps reduce freezer burn on your freezer and frozen food. The white refrigerator features a clean back design that hides the condenser coils, preventing the accumulation of dust and providing you with better performance. The ENERGY STAR certified fridge with energy efficient lighting meets EPA standards and can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. title: Kenmore 36" Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Ice System and 25 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, Stainless Steel
features: ['SLIM FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 25 cubic ft. side-by-side fridge and freezer provides ample fresh and frozen food storage in a slim design, and SpaceSaver ice system saves storage space in the freezer', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Features 15.44 cubic ft. of interior refrigerated space for fresh foods and 9.07 cubic ft. of freezer storage for frozen foods, and has gallon-size door bins for taller, wider items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Easy-to-clean glass shelves give you more shelf space for easier organizing, and TuckAway shelf adjusts to give you 19.75" high storage space for tall containers', "ENERGY EFFICIENT: Long-lasting, energy saving LED lights provide bright lighting to help you find what you need quickly and take stock for your next trip to the store or farmer's market", 'COMPACT SIZE: Measures 35.88" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in smaller kitchens']
description: ['When kitchen space is limited, the Kenmore 25 Cubic Ft. Side-by-Side Refrigerator with SpaceSaver Ice System is the perfect kitchen appliance. This slim refrigerator and freezer combo offers plenty of fresh and frozen food storage, and is perfect for smaller spaces, like apartments, condos, and single family homes. The innovative SpaceSaver Ice System saves valuable frozen storage space with its in-door design. With 15.44 cubic ft. of fresh refrigerated storage and 9.07 cubic ft. of cold, freezer storage, you can stock up on your next run to the grocery store. With the gallon-size door bins, you can store taller and wider food and beverage items, while still having easy access to them. The easy-to-clean glass freezer shelves give you more shelf space for easier organizing. The TuckAway shelf easily adjusts to give you 19.75” high storage space for tall containers, like 2-liter bottles and juice cartons. The Pizza Pocket is the perfect spot to stash two 14" pizza boxes right in the freezer without taking up too much space. For added convenience, the side-by-side refrigerator and freezer features energy-saving dual LED lighting that illuminate the interior to help you quickly find what you’re looking for. The ice and water dispenser is dual pad and allows you to see the spout to accurately fill up containers with small openings. The finger print-resistant stainless steel Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Freezer measures 35.88" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in your kitchen.']

title: Kenmore 30" Top-Freezer Refrigerator with Ice Maker and 18 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, Black
features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 18 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with a pre-installed ice maker is ENERGY STAR certified and provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable split shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items, while the utility bin offers easy-access to your favorite foods', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 29 7/8" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H with a 13.12 cubic ft. fresh food compartment and 5.07 cubic ft. freezer compartment for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and long-lasting LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The convenient ice maker ensures your beverages stay cold, while the large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The ENERGY STAR certified fridge with energy efficient lighting meets EPA standards and can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a black finish measures 29 7/8" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

description: ['The Kenmore 25.5 cu. ft. ENERGY STAR French Door Refrigerator offers plenty of fresh and frozen food storage, while providing your kitchen with a sleek and modern design. For added convenience, the refrigerator features adjustable shelves, gallon-sized door bins, and drawer storage. With 15.6 cubic feet of interior refrigerated space and 9.9 cubic feet of freezer storage, you can stock up at the grocery store without running out of space. It also offers slide-out shelves for customizable food storage that allows for easy access and removal of food essentials. Additional storage features, like gallon-size door bins, allow you to store taller and wider food or beverage products. The drawer style freezer holds all of your frozen essentials, like pizzas, frozen meals, and ice cream. To keep foods fresh, the fridge features a Dual Evaporator design that creates separate cooling climates for the freezer and refrigerator sections. The freezer has a dryer climate, while the fridge has a more humid climate. The humidity controlled drawers keep fruits and veggies fresh. To keep your fridge fresh and odor-free, the refrigerator has an interior deodorizer that gets rid of odors. This refrigerator/freezer combo measures 35.98" W x 30.875" D x 69.80" H']

description: ['You’ll never have to worry about cooling space again with this deluxe bottom-mount apartment refrigerator from Danby. This model has it all including a clear vegetable crisper with glass cover, a convenient CanStor beverage dispenser, two adjustable glass shelves, three integrated door shelves, and an adjustable wire freezer shelf. Although this versatile unit stands just under 60 inches tall and 24 inches in width it offers 9.2 cubic feet (260 liters) of storage area. Your electricity bills will get a much-needed break since this efficient appliance comes with the coveted Energy Star designation and the stylish spotless-steel finish means it’s easy to keep clean. The state-of-the-art frost-free operating system is designed for improved food preservation and effortless maintenance while the bright interior LED light is designed to illuminate without adding heat. In addition, the door comes with an integrated handle and it can be adjusted for left or right-handed opening due to the smart reversible-hinge design. This spacious unit also comes with a 12-month warranty on parts and labor with handy in-home service.']

title: Kenmore 72695 29.5 cu. ft. French Door refrigerator, Stainless Steel
features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR: 29.5 cu. ft. 4-door fridge and freezer provides ample fresh and frozen food storage and filters changed', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: 20.16 cubic feet of interior refrigerated space for fresh foods and 8.93 cubic feet of freezer storage, and has 5 gallon-size door bins for taller and wider food or beverage items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: 3 large flexible shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, and drawer style freezer holds all the frozen essentials', 'KEEPS FOODS FRESH: Triple Evaporator design creates separate cooling climates for the freezer, fridge, and ice compartments, while humidity controlled crispers ensure fresh fruits and veggies', 'ENERGY SAVING 4-DOOR REFRIGERATOR: French door refrigerator measures 35.87" W x 38.14" D x 68.82" H, and is ENERGY STAR certified']
description: ['The Kenmore 29.5 cu. ft. ENERGY STAR 4-Door Smart French Door Refrigerator offers plenty of fresh and frozen food storage, while providing your kitchen with a sleek and modern design. This fridge also features an Active Finish exterior ensuring it is easy to clean and fingerprint smudge resistant. With 20.16 cubic feet of interior refrigerated space and 8.93 cubic feet of freezer storage, you can stock up at the grocery store without running out of space. It also offers three large flexible shelves for customizable food storage that allows for easy access and removal of larger food and beverage items. Additional storage features, like five gallon-size door bins, allow you to store taller and wider food or beverage products. The drawer style freezer holds all of your frozen essentials, like pizzas, frozen meals, and ice cream. To keep foods fresh, the French door style fridge with freezer features a Triple Evaporator design that creates separate cooling climates for the freezer, refrigerator, and ice making compartments. The freezer has a dryer climate, while the fridge has a more humid climate. The humidity controlled crisper drawers keep your fruits and vegetables fresh, crisp, and delicious. This energy saving 4-door refrigerator/freezer combo features a French door style and measures 35.87" W x 38.14" D x 68.82" H, and is ENERGY STAR certified.']

title: Kenmore 36" Side-by-Side Refrigerator and Freezer with 25 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, Stainless Steel
features: ['SLIM FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 25 cubic ft. side-by-side fridge and freezer provides ample fresh and frozen food storage in a slim design and features a dual pad ice and water dispenser.Freezer Capacity:9.11 cubic_feet.Fresh Food Capacity: 15.46 cubic_feet', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Features 15.46 cubic ft. of interior refrigerated space for fresh foods and 9.11 cubic ft. of freezer storage for frozen foods, and has gallon-size door bins for taller, wider items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable, easy-to-clean shelving gives you more shelf space for easier organizing, and can accommodate tall wine bottles and wide juice jugs for customizable food storage', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: Clear bottom plastic crisper drawer is humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slides out easily for removal of produce', 'COMPACT SIZE: Measures 35.5" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in smaller kitchens']
description: ['When kitchen space is limited, the Kenmore 25 Cubic Ft. Slim Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Freezer is the perfect kitchen appliance. This slim refrigerator and freezer combo offers plenty of food storage space while still being perfect for smaller spaces, like apartments, condos, and single family homes. With 15.46 cubic ft. of fresh refrigerated storage space and 9.11 cubic ft. of cold, freezer storage space, you can stock up on your next run to the grocery store. With the gallon-size door bins, you can store taller and wider food and beverage items, while still having easy access to them. The easy-to-clean, adjustable fridge and freezer shelves give you more shelf space for easier organizing. Keep tall containers, like 2-liter bottles and juice cartons, easily stored and accessible with the tall item accommodation door storage. For added convenience, the stainless steel refrigerator and freezer features a clear, humidity controlled crisper drawer for fresh lettuce, celery, and other produce items. The ice and water dispenser is dual pad and has a clear built-in window to view the ice level for ease of use. The Slim Side-by-Side Refrigerator and Freezer measures 35.5" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in your kitchen.']

title: Kenmore 72595 4-Door Smart Refrigerator, 27.8 cu. ft. in Active Finish Stainless Steel-Works with Alexa and enabled with Amazon Dash Replenishment System, includes delivery and hookup
features: ['Item includes room of choice delivery, unboxing, item hook-up and free optional haul-away at checkout', 'Control your Kenmore Smart refrigerator from anywhere with Alexa. Through the app or with voice commands, you can Activate Accela Ice and Max Air Filter, adjust & monitor the temperature, monitor filter life and door open/close status, plus get alerts with any needs. Built-in diagnostics help prevent unnecessary service by making maintenance easier.', 'This Kenmore Smart fridge has 28.7 cu. ft. of interior space, plenty of room to stock up favorite snacks, leftovers and household staples. Adjustable interior storage makes putting the groceries away hassle-free while the dual freezer drawers make it easy to stash and organize frozen foods. Humidity-controlled crispers and a gourmet full-width pantry drawer keep fresh foods and deli favorites close at hand and at ideal temperatures. A Slide Away shelf gives you extra space when you need it for taller items.', 'The dual freezer drawers make organizing your frozen foods simple. The top drawer is perfect for household staples and smaller items while the bottom drawer has space enough for a large turkey and prepped meals.', 'Cool Edge direct door cooling keeps a steady supply of cold air circulating throughout your fridge, including bins and pantry drawers, to keep your foods at the ideal temperature. description: ['Keep your refrigerated and frozen food items at the correct temperature with the Kenmore 18-Cubic Feet Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This Kenmore top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic feet of interior space, perfect for stocking up on snacks, leftovers, lunches and cans of soda for the home or office. Keep delicious leftovers right next to lunch bags and other groceries, and stash crisp produce in the humidity controlled crisper. Features full-width adjustable glass shelves and 2 clear plastic crisper drawers for fresh and crisp fruits and vegetables. The refrigerator features slide-out glass storage shelves for easy access and removal of pies, cakes, casseroles, and larger food items. With the adjustable shelving, you get near-limitless interior organization options. With the convenient door storage there’s no more trying to puzzle out how to fit food in the fridge. Gallon door bins make it easy to store tall items and beverages alongside your favorite sauces, dressings and other ingredients. Tall item accommodation on the bottom shelf means more space for bottles of wine and water; no more trying to shove things wherever they\'ll fit. The roomy freezer can hold all of your frozen food neatly. No more digging through a pile of frozen food for a bag of peas. This Kenmore frost-free top freezer helps you keep foods nice and organized with two door bins and a single shelf. Features a clean back design that hides the condenser coils, preventing the accumulation of dust and providing you with better refrigerating performance. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. Freezer does not have an icemaker. This Kenmore top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic feet of interior space, perfect for stocking up on snacks, leftovers, lunches and cans of soda for the home or office. Keep delicious leftovers right next to lunch bags and other groceries, and stash crisp produce in the humidity controlled crisper. Features full-width adjustable glass shelves and 2 clear plastic crisper drawers for fresh and crisp fruits and vegetables. The refrigerator features slide-out glass storage shelves for easy access and removal of pies, cakes, casseroles, and larger food items. With the adjustable shelving, you get near-limitless interior organization options. With the convenient door storage there’s no more trying to puzzle out how to fit food in the fridge. Gallon door bins make it easy to store tall items and beverages alongside your favorite sauces, dressings and other ingredients. Tall item accommodation on the bottom shelf means more space for bottles of wine and water; no more trying to shove things wherever they\'ll fit. The roomy freezer can hold all of your frozen food neatly. No more digging through a pile of frozen food for a bag of peas. This Kenmore frost-free top freezer helps you keep foods nice and organized with two door bins and a single shelf. Features a clean back design that hides the condenser coils, preventing the accumulation of dust and providing you with better refrigerating performance. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit.Freezer does not have an icemaker. title: LG SIGNATURE 31 cu. ft. Smart wi-fi Enabled InstaView™ Door-in-Door® Refrigerator
description: ['LG SIGNATURE \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInstaView™ Door-in-Door® \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAuto Open Door™ \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTextured Steel™ Finish \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFresh Filter \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCustom Chill™ LG SIGNATURE stays true to the essence, delivering a new sense of life for the most discerning individual. InstaView™ Door-in-Door® has a sleek mirrored glass panel that illuminates with two quick knocks, allowing you to see inside the easy access compartment without ever opening the door, reducing cold air loss to help keep food fresher longer. Auto Open Door™ feature is a smart sensor detector at the foot of the refrigerator that opens the door automatically. Just step on the "Door Open" light projection on the floor in front of the refrigerator and the door gently opens. Full stainless steel body with a scratch-resistant textured finish makes for an impeccable exterior design, enhancing its minimalist style to the fullest. The wide and deep versatile pantry is available with different temperature settings for storing a wide range of foods from meats to fresh produce. Experience true satisfaction with LG SmartThinQ® technology that allows remote management of key refrigerator features. For added convenience, the refrigerator and freezer combo features bright, energy efficient LED lighting that illuminates the interior to help you quickly find what you’re looking for. The ice maker is internal for a clean look that is complemented by the stainless steel finish. The Slim Side-by-Side Refrigerator and Freezer measures 35.5" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in your kitchen.']

Features include adjustable shelving, tall bottle storage, and a crisper drawer. At under 57 inches tall and less than 24 inches wide, this unit fits through most tight doorways and can be navigated down a narrow staircase. At 95 pounds, two adults can easily manage moving this refrigerator. Left-handed or right-handed opening is your choice with the reversible door hinge. Combined with the smooth back design, placement will be effortless. Plus, Energy Star efficiency will help you save on your energy bill. Package Content: refrigerator/freezermanualwarranty"]

title: 30 cu. ft. Smart wi-fi Enabled Door-in-Door® Refrigerator with Craft Ice™ Maker
description: ['30 cu. ft. Capacity \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDoor-in-Door® with Adjustable Bins \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCool Guard \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTall Ice & Water Dispenser® with Measured Fill \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDual Ice Maker with Craft Ice™ \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThinQ® Technology with ThinQ Care Discover ThinQ Care within the ThinQ app -- proactive smart alerts to keep your appliances running smoothly. Get notifications about usage, maintenance, plus early diagnosis right on your smartphone. With 30 cu. ft. of more usable space*, you can save time and stock up on your club store fresh and frozen faves in one trip with room to store them all when you get home. *Compared to LG\'s standard width French door refrigerator. Offering quick and easy access to favorite foods, the popular Door-in-Door® design gets even better with adjustable bins that smoothly glide up and down to fit snacks and drinks of all sizes. Cool Guard metal interior panel wall helps maintain cold air while adding a premium look. LG’s exclusive Craft Ice™ slow melting round ice maker automatically makes batches of three ice spheres per day without the work of time consuming molds. Give your beverages the perfect ice for next level entertaining, from craft cocktails & whiskey to soft drinks, lemonade, even iced coffee. To get even more Craft Ice™, activate Craft Ice+ in the ThinQ® App to make slow-melting ice twice as fast. *Shape and clarity of ice will be impacted when Craft Ice+ is activated; may vary with settings, home use and water supply. Finally, an ice & water dispenser that can accommodate just about any bottle size. With the convenient Measured Fill feature, you can also dispense exact amounts of filtered water in ounces (4,8,16, or 32). Ice makers are great, but not if it means you can\'t fit all of your food in the fridge. The Slim SpacePlus® Ice System provides more shelf space and allows even more space for door bins. *Standard width french door refrigerator, excludes other LG manufactured products. Part of the ThinQ® app, Smart Learner analyzes habits to anticipate temperature, ice & energy needs. Nothing is more frustrating than an appliance that doesn’t fit. We’ll help you find the right one for your space. The interior layout makes it effortless to maintain a neat and organized cooler. Specially designed, the best part about the Danby 10.1 Cubic Foot Apartment-Size Fridge is it's built to be maintenance-free. Never worry about freezer burn thanks to the automatic defrost that prevents ice build up. Controlled airflow gives your groceries a longer shelf-life without loss of storage capacity. Spoil your food and yourself with Danby's Apartment Refrigerator."]

description: ["Make food storage even easier with the Kenmore Finger Print Resistant Stainless Steel 25.6 cu. ft. French Door Bottom-Freezer Refrigerator. You'll be able to give your favorite foods the space and care they need. Outfitted with everything from gallon-sized door bins that give you space for juice, milk and tall bottles to a full-width gourmet pantry drawer that's perfect for pizzas, platters, trays and more, you'll love the space you have to organize your fresh and frozen favorite items. Your food will have more than enough breathing room inside the Kenmore 25.6 cu. ft. french door bottom-freezer refrigerator. A larger capacity means you'll be able to fit all your favorite snacks and meals inside this spacious fridge. If you're hosting a birthday party or potluck dinner, you'll certainly appreciate the full-width, gourmet pantry drawer that's perfect for storing party platters, pizzas, pies, fruit and veggies trays and more. Jugs of juice, gallons of milk, and more, this refrigerator's gallon-sized door bins give you space to fit just about any-sized drink container which means no more having to shove bottles in to make them fit. With the dual evaporator, you'll be able to make sure everything inside stays fresh longe becuse it produces separate cooling environments, creating ideal temperatures and humidity levels in both the refrigerator and freezer. Fill up your glass of water and chill it quickly and easily, thanks an exterior ice dispenser that makes both crushed and cubed ice. Take stock of the frozen foods you have (and what you need to pick up) simply by sliding out this refrigerator's bottom-mount freezer drawer. The freezer is equipped with Frost-Free technology, so your frozen food stays fresher longer."]

description: ["With the Kenmore 26.1 cubic feet French Door Refrigerator with Bottom-Freezer, not only are you getting an exceptionally well-made and reliable appliance, you're also getting an appliance that takes care of all of your family's food storage needs. You'll be amazed at the storage capacity of this large fridge. The refrigerator has dual evaporators that cool the refrigerator and freezer separately to keep each section at the ideal temperature and humidity level. For easy access to your bulkier food items, gallon-sized door bins give you space for containers of juice, milk, and taller items. The full width pantry drawer has room for extra-large items, like veggie trays and party platters. With its easy-care wipe clean exterior and interior tempered glass shelves, this French door refrigerator is a welcome addition to any kitchen space. For convenient frozen food storage, the frost-free freezer protects your frozen leftovers from freezer burn and keeps food fresher longer. You'll always have ice at the ready with a built-in ice maker. A built-in ice maker keeps fresh ice at your fingertips, so you can whip up smoothies, cocktails, and more in a flash. The French door refrigerator measures 35.38” W x 35.9” D x 68.58” H."]

Through innovative, reliable products and services; talented people; a responsible approach to business and global citizenship; and collaboration with their partners and customers, SAMSUNG is taking the world in imaginative new directions.  The Samsung Philosophy. At SAMSUNG, they follow a simple business philosophy: to devote their talent and technology to creating superior products and services that contribute to a better global society. Every day, their people bring this philosophy to life. Their leaders search for the brightest talent from around the world, and give them the resources they need to be the best at what they do. The result is that all of their products - from memory chips that help businesses store vital knowledge to mobile phones that connect people across continents - have the power to enrich lives. And that's what making a better global society is all about.  Their Vision. Their Mission. SAMSUNG is guided by a singular vision: to lead the digital convergence movement. They believe that through technology innovation today, they will find the solutions they need to address the challenges of tomorrow. From technology, comes opportunity - for businesses to grow, for citizens in emerging markets to prosper by tapping into the digital economy, and for people to invent new possibilities. It's their aim to develop innovative technologies and efficient processes that create new markets, enrich people's lives and continue to make Samsung a trusted market leader. title: Kenmore 30" Top-Freezer Refrigerator with Ice Maker and 18 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, Stainless Steel
features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 18 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with a pre-installed ice maker is ENERGY STAR certified and provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable split shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items, while the utility bin offers easy-access to your favorite foods', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 29 7/8" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H with a 13.12 cubic ft. fresh food compartment and 5.07 cubic ft. freezer compartment for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and long-lasting LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The convenient ice maker ensures your beverages stay cold, while the large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The ENERGY STAR certified fridge with energy efficient lighting meets EPA standards and can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a finger-print resistant stainless steel finish measures 29 7/8" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

title: Kenmore 33" Top-Freezer Refrigerator with 21 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, White
features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 21 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with door storage provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Full-width shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'LED LIGHTING: Long-lasting LED lights provide warm, natural lighting to help you find what you need quickly and take stock of what you need on your next trip to the grocery store', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 32 7/8" W x 33.8" D x 67.25" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 21 cubic ft. of interior space and energy efficient LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features full-width shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The 2 clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh. With the refrigerator\'s door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The fridge can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a white finish measures 32 7/8" W x 33.8" D x 67.25" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

title: Samsung RF24FSEDBSR Stainless Steel Counter Depth 4-Door Refrigerator, 24 Cubic Feet
features: ['4-Door Counter-Depth Design', 'Twin Cooling Plus', 'High Capacity-24 cu.-feet', 'Ice Master Ice Maker in the Refrigerator', 'FlexZone Drawer with TemperatureControl and Smart Divider']
description: ['Amazon.com', "The Samsung Stainless Steel Counter Depth 4-Door Refrigerator with FlexZone Drawer is ideal for those who love to cook and entertain. This modern, four-door refrigerator features a total capacity of 24 cubic feet* — enough room for up to 24 bags of groceries**. Separate airflows in the refrigerator and freezer help keep food fresh, while the FlexZone drawer lets you store food in four different temperature zones. The refrigerator includes an external filtered water dispenser and an in-fridge ice maker that can produce up to 5.9 pounds of ice daily. And with five shelves, two humidity-controlled crispers, and six door bins, you'll have plenty of room for all your favorite drinks, party platters, and leftovers.", 'Fridge sits at the same depth as your counter, creating a built-in look and giving you more space in your kitchen.', 'View larger', '.', 'FlexZone drawer lets you store food at four different temperature zones.', 'View larger', '.', 'Counter-Depth Design for Built-in Look', 'The stainless steel refrigerator features a modern design, with twin French doors, a FlexZone Drawer, and a large pullout freezer drawer. It sits at the same depth as your counter, creating a built-in look and giving you more space in your kitchen. Stainless steel accents on the interior shelving and door bins complement the exterior for a sleek, polished look.', 'High Capacity Saves You Trips to the Market', 'With a total capacity of 24 cubic feet*, the Samsung Stainless Steel Counter Depth Refrigerator provides enough space to hold up to 24 bags of groceries**. Two humidity-controlled crispers help keep produce fresh, while a three-way shelf made of tempered glass can slide in or flip up for even more storage space. The refrigerator also includes six clear door bins — three 1-gallon bins on the right door and three regular-size bins on the left.', 'Twin Cooling Plus System For Fresher Produce', "Samsung's Twin Cooling Plus System helps keep food fresh with two separate airflows for the fridge and freezer. Refrigerator air is kept at higher, near-commercial grade humidity levels to prevent perishable fruits and vegetables from spoiling, while cooler, drier freezer air results in less freezer burn for better-tasting frozen food.", 'FlexZone Drawer Keeps Food at Proper Temperature', 'The FlexZone drawer with an adjustable smart divider lets you create compartments with four separate temperature zones for meat, drinks, snacks, and party dishes. The FlexZone drawer features an EZ-Open handle that allows you to effortlessly open a fully loaded drawer. Plus, its counter-height location makes it easy for children to retrieve their favorite snacks.', 'Produces More Than 5 Pounds of Ice Daily', "Ideal for parties and barbecues, the refrigerator's Ice Master can produce up to 5.9 pounds of ice per day and can store up to 2.9 pounds. Its space-saving design leaves more room in the refrigerator for your party platters and leftovers. An external water dispenser delivers filtered water and your choice of crushed or cubed ice and an indicator light lets you know when the filter needs to be changed.", 'Energy-Efficient Lighting', 'High-efficiency LED lighting in the fridge and freezer brightens every corner so you can quickly spot what you need. LED lights emit less heat, making them more energy efficient than traditional bulbs. title: Kenmore 73105 French Door Smart Refrigerator, 27.9 cu. ft. in Active Finish Stainless Steel-Works with Alexa and enabled with Amazon Dash Replenishment System, includes delivery and hookup
features: ['Item includes room of choice delivery, unboxing, item hook-up and free optional haul-away at checkout', 'Control your Kenmore Smart refrigerator from anywhere with Alexa. Through the app or with voice commands, you can Activate Accela Ice and Max Air Filter, adjust & monitor the temperature, monitor filter life and door open/close status, plus get alerts with any needs. Built-in diagnostics help prevent unnecessary service by making maintenance easier.', 'This Kenmore Smart fridge has 27.9 cu. ft. of interior space, plenty of room to stock up favorite snacks, leftovers and household staples. Adjustable interior storage makes putting the groceries away hassle-free while the dual freezer drawers make it easy to stash and organize frozen foods.', 'The dual freezer drawers make organizing your frozen foods simple. The top drawer is perfect for household staples and smaller items while the bottom drawer has space enough for a large turkey and prepped meals.', 'Cool Edge direct door cooling keeps a steady supply of cold air circulating throughout your fridge, including bins and pantry drawers, to keep your foods at the ideal temperature. Multi air flow technology works with the CleanFlow Air Filter to circulate fresh air through a charcoal filter, removing food odors and keeping your fridge interior nice and fresh for your fresh foods.', "Grab fresh clear water right from the in-door dispenser. A deluxe water filter helps remove contaminates and give you fresh-tasting water and ice. Accela Ice gives you the option to speed up ice production, perfect for when you have guests over, while the slim in-door ice maker won't hog fridge space.", 'Humidity-controlled crispers and a gourmet full-width pantry drawer keep fresh foods and deli favorites close at hand and at ideal temperatures. A Slide Away shelf gives you extra space when you need it for taller items.']
description: ['Bring home the bacon and keep it fresh with the Kenmore 27.9 cu. ft. Smart french door refrigerator. Designed to be compatible with your Amazon Alexa™, this Kenmore Smart fridge makes it easy to keep tabs on your fridge status and make lists with Alexa or the Kenmore Smart app. With the Kenmore Smart App and Alexa voice controls, you can set up automatic replacement through Amazon Dash Replenishment for ultimate convenience. Pairing modern conveniences with smart technology, this french door fridge has both the space and the smarts to keep your household running on time and well-stocked with fresh foods.']
