Boasting 11 cubic-feet (311 liters) of storage and cooling space, it features three chrome-trimmed tempered glass shelves and five integrated door shelves for maximum storage versatility. There’s more than enough room for larger bottles and the spacious unit helps keep electricity bills in check with its Energy Star rating and state-of-the-art mechanical thermostat. Maintenance and cleaning are as simple as can be with the automatic defrost system. It also includes an efficient and reliable interior white LED light. This model (DAR110A3MDB) is built for convenience as the reversible door hinge allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening.']

description: ['24 cu. ft. Capacity \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInstaView™ Door-in-Door® with adjustable bin \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDual Ice maker with Craft Ice™ \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTall Ice & Water Dispenser® with Measured Fill \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInnovative Cooling Features \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCool Guard Discover ThinQ Care within the ThinQ app -- proactive smart alerts to keep your appliances running smoothly. Get notifications about usage, maintenance, plus early diagnosis right on your smartphone.* With the Large-Capacity 24 cu. ft. refrigerator, you have even more usable space* allowing you to store more food than ever before. Plus, the Slim SpacePlus® Ice System is built into the refrigerator door to help create the most shelf space* and allows even more space for door bins. *Compared to LG\'s standard width French door refrigerator. *Standard width French door refrigerator, excludes other LG manufactured products. Combining innovation and distinctive design, the InstaView™ Door-in-Door® refrigerator will enhance even the most beautifully crafted kitchen. The sleek tinted glass panel illuminates with two quick knocks, so you can see inside the easy access compartment without opening the door, reducing cold air loss to help keep food fresher longer. LG’s exclusive Craft Ice™ slow melting round ice maker automatically makes batches of three ice spheres per day without the work of time consuming molds. Give your beverages the perfect ice for next level entertaining, from craft cocktails & whiskey to soft drinks, lemonade, even iced coffee. To get even more Craft Ice™, activate Craft Ice+ in the ThinQ® App to make slow-melting ice twice as fast. *Shape and clarity of ice will be impacted when Craft Ice+ is activated; may vary with settings, home use and water supply. Finally, an ice & water dispenser that can accommodate just about any bottle size. With the convenient Measured Fill feature, you can also dispense exact amounts of filtered water in ounces (4,8,16, or 32). Only LG offers 3 cooling technologies that work together to extend the life of fruits and vegetables and help keep all foods fresh. Linear Cooling keeps temperatures within 1°F of the setting, Smart Cooling uses sensors and vents for total cooling control, and Door Cooling+ delivers blasts of cool air to all areas of the refrigerator. *Than other LG models. Based on LG internal tests between LFXS30796D and LRFDS3006S. Cool Guard metal interior panel wall helps maintain cold air while adding a premium look. PrintProof™ finish resists fingerprints and smudges to keep your kitchen looking its best. Available in stainless and black stainless steel, it provides a premium look and professional-grade durability—without the need for special cleaners or constant attention. Plus, it easily wipes clean with a soft, dry cloth. Part of the ThinQ® app, Smart Learner analyzes habits to anticipate temperature, ice & energy needs. Nothing is more frustrating than an appliance that doesn’t fit. We’ll help you find the right one for your space. title: Kenmore 36" Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Ice System and 25 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, White
features: ['SLIM FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 25 cubic ft. side-by-side fridge and freezer provides ample fresh and frozen food storage in a slim design, and SpaceSaver ice system saves storage space in the freezer', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Features 15.44 cubic ft. of interior refrigerated space for fresh foods and 9.07 cubic ft. of freezer storage for frozen foods, and has gallon-size door bins for taller, wider items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Easy-to-clean glass shelves give you more shelf space for easier organizing, and TuckAway shelf adjusts to give you 19.75" high storage space for tall containers', "ENERGY EFFICIENT: Long-lasting, energy saving LED lights provide bright lighting to help you find what you need quickly and take stock for your next trip to the store or farmer's market", 'COMPACT SIZE: Measures 35.88" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in smaller kitchens']
description: ['When kitchen space is limited, the Kenmore 25 Cubic Ft. Side-by-Side Refrigerator with SpaceSaver Ice System is the perfect kitchen appliance. This slim refrigerator and freezer combo offers plenty of fresh and frozen food storage, and is perfect for smaller spaces, like apartments, condos, and single family homes. The innovative SpaceSaver Ice System saves valuable frozen storage space with its in-door design. With 15.44 cubic ft. of fresh refrigerated storage and 9.07 cubic ft. of cold, freezer storage, you can stock up on your next run to the grocery store. With the gallon-size door bins, you can store taller and wider food and beverage items, while still having easy access to them. The easy-to-clean glass freezer shelves give you more shelf space for easier organizing. The TuckAway shelf easily adjusts to give you 19.75” high storage space for tall containers, like 2-liter bottles and juice cartons. The Pizza Pocket is the perfect spot to stash two 14" pizza boxes right in the freezer without taking up too much space. For added convenience, the side-by-side refrigerator and freezer features energy-saving dual LED lighting that illuminate the interior to help you quickly find what you’re looking for. The ice and water dispenser is dual pad and allows you to see the spout to accurately fill up containers with small openings. The white Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Freezer measures 35.88" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in your kitchen.']

title: LG LFX31935 31 Cu. Ft. French Door Refrigerator with Blast Chiller and Three-Layer Freezer, Stainless Steel
features: ['Super-Capacity (31 cu. ft.)', 'Slim SpacePlus Ice System', 'Smart Cooling Plus System']
description: ["LG Stainless Steel Bottom Freezer Freestanding Refrigerator LFX31935ST. Super capacity, with 31 cu. ft., you can store more food than ever before. And keep it all fresher, longer. The compartment cools at an accelerated rate and swirls the air inside to keep the temperature evenly distributed. A 12 oz. can of soda or beer can be chilled to ice cold in five minutes. In eight minutes, the same can happen with a bottle of wine or two soda cans. Ice makers are great, but not if it means you can't fit all of your food in the fridge. The Slim SpacePlus Ice System provides more shelf space and allows even more space for door bins. Smart Cooling Plus technology is designed to maintain superior conditions within the refrigerator. The Linear Compressor and Dual Evaporators react quickly to humidity and temperature levels and help keep your food fresher, longer. Meanwhile, strategically-placed vents in every section surround your food with cool, fresh air no matter where you put it. When you buy a refrigerator, you don't want to worry that it won't last. Because the Linear Compressor motor uses fewer moving parts and operates more efficiently. LG confidently backs the motor with a 10-year warranty. The Smart Pull Handle makes opening and closing the freezer quick and easy. All it takes is a simple lift of the handle for effortless access to your freezer. The 3-Tier Organization Freezer system can keep food organized and easily accessible. Now you can prioritize what's in your freezer so you can find anything fast. Your food isn't the only thing that stays fresh. Their 3-layer Fresh Air Filter with forced air circulation and dedicated fan pushes cleaner, deodorized air into the fridge. From pitchers to pint glasses, finally an ice and water dispenser that can accommodate just about any container. The water- and ice-dispenser in this LG 3-Door refrigerator is one of the tallest around, measuring in at an ultra-accommodating 12.6 inches. Save your produce and stop your searching."]

title: Kenmore 36" Side-by-Side Refrigerator and Freezer with 25 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, Black
features: ['SLIM FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 25 cubic ft. side-by-side fridge and freezer provides ample fresh and frozen food storage in a slim design and features a dual pad ice and water dispenser', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Features 15.46 cubic ft. of interior refrigerated space for fresh foods and 9.11 cubic ft. of freezer storage for frozen foods, and has gallon-size door bins for taller, wider items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable, easy-to-clean shelving gives you more shelf space for easier organizing, and can accommodate tall wine bottles and wide juice jugs for customizable food storage', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: Clear bottom plastic crisper drawer is humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slides out easily for removal of produce', 'COMPACT SIZE: Measures 35.5" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in smaller kitchens']
description: ['When kitchen space is limited, the Kenmore 25 Cubic Ft. Slim Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Freezer is the perfect kitchen appliance. This slim refrigerator and freezer combo offers plenty of food storage space while still being perfect for smaller spaces, like apartments, condos, and single family homes. With 15.46 cubic ft. of fresh refrigerated storage space and 9.11 cubic ft. of cold, freezer storage space, you can stock up on your next run to the grocery store. With the gallon-size door bins, you can store taller and wider food and beverage items, while still having easy access to them. The easy-to-clean, adjustable fridge and freezer shelves give you more shelf space for easier organizing. Keep tall containers, like 2-liter bottles and juice cartons, easily stored and accessible with the tall item accommodation door storage. For added convenience, the black refrigerator and freezer features a clear, humidity controlled crisper drawer for fresh lettuce, celery, and other produce items. The ice and water dispenser is dual pad and has a clear built-in window to view the ice level for ease of use. The Slim Side-by-Side Refrigerator and Freezer measures 35.5" W x 33.81" D x 68.63" H for a perfect fit in your kitchen.']

features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 18 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with energy efficient LED lighting provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable split shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items, while the utility bin offers easy-access to your favorite foods', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 29.76" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H with a 13.12 cubic ft. fresh food compartment and 5.07 cubic ft. freezer compartment for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and energy efficient LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The fridge can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a finger-print resistant stainless steel finish measures 29.76" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

description: ['Product Description', 'Having separate fridge and freezer units is definitely the way to go these days. You get that convenient combination and much more with this splendid dual-door compact refrigerator by Danby. This model offers 3.1 cu. ft. (87 L) of cooling and freezing capacity and is Energy-Star compliant to help keep electricity costs as low as possible. The popular appliance is a perfect match for apartments, rec-rooms, bars, cottages and offices. It has a high-tech mechanical thermostat to make sure your foods are always stored at the correct temperature and has a handy manual defrosting system. It comes with an intelligent reversible-door feature which allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This glamorous fridge/freezer is a breeze to keep clean due to the stunning spotless-steel finish. Inside the appliance you’ll find a bright interior light as well as a see-through vegetable crisper with glass cover and plenty of space for tall bottles. The integrated door handle adds another touch of class.', 'From the Manufacturer', 'Having separate fridge and freezer units is definitely the way to go these days. You get that convenient combination and much more with this splendid dual-door compact refrigerator by Danby. This model offers 3.1 cu. ft. of cooling and freezing capacity and is Energy-Star compliant to help keep electricity costs as low as possible. It also uses environmentally friendly R600a refrigerant as the coolant for the unit. The popular appliance is a perfect match for apartments, rec-rooms, bars, cottages and offices. It has a high-tech mechanical thermostat to make sure your foods are always stored at the correct temperature and has a handy cycle defrosting system. It comes with an intelligent reversible-door feature which allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This glamorous fridge/freezer is a breeze to keep clean due to the stunning spotless-steel finish. title: Summit FFBF249SS 24" Counter Depth ENERGY STAR Bottom Freezer Refrigerator with Digital Control Panel, Stainless Steel
features: ['ENERGY STAR certified to save on energy bills and maximize efficiency', 'Slim 24” W x 25 ¼” D footprint offers generous storage capacity in a counter deep fit', 'Digital thermostat for each section with an innovative control panel', 'Made in Europe with stainless steel doors for a modern look', 'Adaptive intelligent technology includes innovative sensors to adjust performance based on your habits']
description: ['Summit Appliance offers a unique collection of European ENERGY STAR qualified bottom freezer refrigerators designed to bring true luxury into smaller kitchen spaces. Model FFBF249SS is sized at 74 3/8” H x 23 5/8” W x 24 5/8” D, with a generous 11.6 cu.ft. interior capacity. The stainless steel doors come in a modern curved design, with professional style handles and a platinum cabinet to complete the look. The digital control panel is located on the outer door, allowing you to manage both the refrigerator and freezer temperatures without opening the unit and exposing stored items to room temperature. The refrigerator interior includes adjustable spill-proof glass shelves, adjustable door racks, a large humidity controlled crisper, scalloped wine shelf, and a “ZeroZone” deli drawer for meats and cheeses that might need colder storage temperature. The lower freezer compartment includes three slide-out storage baskets that help to protect stored items when the door is open. The FFBF249SS utilizes adaptive intelligent technology that allows the unit to adjust to its users’ habits for a more efficient performance. The auto defrost refrigerator section and frost-free freezer help to minimize user maintenance. Additional features include LED lighting, a child lock on the control panel, a removable multibox storage container with an air-tight seal, and audible and visual high temperature and open door alarms. PLEASE NOTE: This unit has a right hand door swing and cannot be reversed by the user. For this unit with a left hand door swing, see the FFBF249SSLHD.']

title: Kenmore 30" Top-Freezer Refrigerator with Ice Maker and 18 Cubic Ft. Total Capacity, Stainless Steel
features: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 18 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with energy efficient LED lighting and pre-installed ice maker provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items.Frequency : 60 hertz', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable split shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items, while the utility bin offers easy-access to your favorite foods', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 29.76" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H with a 13.12 cubic ft. fresh food compartment and 5.07 cubic ft. freezer compartment for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and energy efficient LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, there’s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The fridge can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors and comes with a built-in ice maker to keep your beverages cool. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a finger-print resistant stainless steel finish measures 29.76" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

description: ['Amazon.com', "REVIEW: The Samsung Stainless Steel 4-Door Refrigerator with Automatic Sparkling Water Dispenser is ideal for large families and those who love to cook and entertain. With a capacity of 31 cubic feet, this modern, four-door refrigerator can hold up to 31 bags of groceries*. It features a built-in sparkling and still water dispenser powered by SodaStream and an in-fridge ice maker that makes up to 10 pounds of ice daily. Separate air flows in the refrigerator and freezer help keep food fresher, while the FlexZone drawer lets you store food at four different temperature zones. And with five shelves, two humidity-controlled crispers, and six door bins, you'll have plenty of room for all your favorite drinks, party platters, and leftovers.", 'Four-door refrigerator can hold up to 31 bags of groceries*.', 'View larger', '.', 'Features two humidity-controlled crispers, a three-way shelf made of tempered glass, and three 1-gallon door bins.', 'View larger', '.', 'Enjoy chilled stillor sparkling water.', 'View larger', '.', 'Enjoy Refreshing Sparkling Water Anytime', 'Great for sparkling water lovers, a built-in dispenser on the outside of the fridge powered by SodaStream delivers chilled sparkling or still water. This convenient feature saves you money and creates less waste than buying bottled sparkling water. The dispenser also produces your choice of crushed or cubed ice.', 'Holds up to 31 Bags of Groceries*', 'Samsung refrigerators are engineered to offer more space inside with the same outside dimensions as traditional models. With a total capacity of 31 cubic feet, the Samsung Stainless Steel 4-Door Refrigerator provides enough space to hold up to 31 bags of groceries. Two humidity-controlled crispers help keep produce fresh, while a three-way shelf made of tempered glass can slide in or flip up to provide more space for tall or oversized items. The refrigerator also includes six clear door bins — three 1-gallon bins on the right door and three regular-size bins on the left.', 'Twin Cooling Plus System For Fresher Produce', "Samsung's Twin Cooling Plus System helps keep food fresh with two separate airflows for the fridge and freezer. Refrigerator air is kept at higher, near-commercial grade humidity levels to prevent perishable fruits and vegetables from spoiling, while cooler, drier freezer air results in less freezer burn for better-tasting frozen food.", 'Produces up to 10 Pounds of Ice Daily', "Ideal for parties and barbecues, the refrigerator's Ice Master makes up to 10 pounds of ice per day and can store up to 4.2 pounds. Plus, its counter-height location makes it easy for children to retrieve their favorite snacks.', 'Four-Door Design with Stainless Steel Accents', 'The stainless steel refrigerator features a modern design with French doors, a counter-level FlexZone drawer, and a large pullout freezer. LED lights save space and emit less heat than traditional incandescent bulbs, making them a more energy-efficient choice. title: 30 cu. ft. Smart wi-fi Enabled Refrigerator with Craft Ice™ Maker
features: ['30 Cu.Ft.', 'Door-in-Door', 'Full-Convert Drawer With 5 Temperature Settings', 'Tall Ice & Water Dispenser With Measured Fill']
description: ['30 cu. ft. Capacity \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDoor-in-Door® \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFull-Convert™ drawer with 5 temperature settings \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTall Ice & Water Dispenser® with Measured Fill \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDual Ice Maker with Craft Ice™ \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThinQ® Technology with ThinQ Care Discover ThinQ Care within the ThinQ app -- proactive smart alerts to keep your appliances running smoothly. Get notifications about usage, maintenance, plus early diagnosis right on your smartphone. With 30 cu. ft. of more usable space*, you can save time and stock up on your club store fresh and frozen faves in one trip with room to store them all when you get home. *Compared to LG\'s standard width French door refrigerator. Get more usable space but keep it flexible with the Full-Convert™ Drawer – now with five temperature settings to fit your family\'s needs. Choose from Chilled Wine, Deli/Snacks, Cold Drinks, Meat/Seafood, and Freeze settings. Plus, adjustable dividers keep everything organized. Offering quick and easy access to favorite foods, the popular Door-in-Door® design gets even better with adjustable bins that smoothly glide up and down to fit snacks and drinks of all sizes. LG’s exclusive Craft Ice™ slow melting round ice maker automatically makes batches of three ice spheres per day without the work of time consuming molds. Give your beverages the perfect ice for next level entertaining, from craft cocktails & whiskey to soft drinks, lemonade, even iced coffee. To get even more Craft Ice™, activate Craft Ice+ in the ThinQ® App to make slow-melting ice twice as fast. *Shape and clarity of ice will be impacted when Craft Ice+ is activated; may vary with settings, home use and water supply. Finally, an ice & water dispenser that can accommodate just about any bottle size. With the convenient Measured Fill feature, you can also dispense exact amounts of filtered water in ounces (4,8,16, or 32). Ice makers are great, but not if it means you can\'t fit all of your food in the fridge. The Slim SpacePlus® Ice System provides more shelf space and allows even more space for door bins. *Standard width french door refrigerator, excludes other LG manufactured products. Part of the ThinQ® app, Smart Learner analyzes habits to anticipate temperature, ice & energy needs. Nothing is more frustrating than an appliance that doesn’t fit. We’ll help you find the right one for your space. Enjoy a built-in look with the counter depth feature on this LG refrigerator. Thanks to its slightly shallower depth, it can stand flush with your counter top for a sleek look. Combining innovation and distinctive design, the InstaView™ Door-in-Door® refrigerator will enhance even the most beautifully crafted kitchen. The sleek tinted glass panel illuminates with two quick knocks, so you can see inside the easy access compartment without opening the door, reducing cold air loss to help keep food fresher longer. Now you can have all of the things you love about stainless, without the need for special cleaners or constant attention. LG’s PrintProof™ fingerprint and smudge resistant finish easily wipes clean with a soft, dry cloth for a distinctive kitchen that handles real-life in style. Located in the top of the fresh food section, the Door Cooling + vent extends the reach of LG’s Smart Cooling system. Blasts of cool air reach all areas of the refrigerator—including the door—to help maintain consistent temperatures from top to bottom. It helps keep all foods fresh and flavorful and keeps produce fresh up to 2X longer.* *Than other LG models. Based on LG internal tests between LFXS30796D and LRFDS3006S and in combination with Linear Cooling and Smart Cooling technologies. description: ['The Kenmore 25. 5 Cubic Feet French Door Refrigerator and Freezer with Dual Ice Makers is perfect for storing fresh groceries for the whole family while staying organized. This Kenmore large capacity French door refrigerator has 25. 5 cubic feet of interior space, perfect for stocking up on snacks, leftovers, lunches and frozen foods. Keep delicious leftovers right next to lunch bags and other groceries, and stash crisp produce in the temperature-controlled drawer. Features flexible glass storage shelves that slide in and out with ease. Store more fresh foods and cold drinks in this accommodating fridge/freezer combo. With the convenient door storage there’s no more trying to puzzle out how to fit food in the fridge. Generously sized gallon door bins make it easy to store tall items and beverages alongside your favorite sauces, dressings and other ingredients. Tall item accommodation on the bottom shelf means more space for bottles of wine and water; no more trying to shove things wherever they\'ll fit. Featuring a roomy 7. 8 cubic feet freezer, this frost-free freezer can hold all of your frozen food neatly and at the right temperature. No more digging through a pile of frozen food for a bag of peas. The frost-free freezer helps reduce freezer burn on your freezer and the food stored inside it. Keep the ice flowing with the dual ice makers, dispensed from the door and located in the freezer. The extra ice storage means you’ll never run out of ice on hot summer days. A dual evaporator cools the refrigerator and freezer separately to keep each side at their ideal temperature. This Energy Star qualified fridge will help impact your energy bill while reducing your carbon footprint. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. DIMENSIONS: 35. 9" L x 35. 9" W x 69. 8" H STORAGE SPACE: 25. 5 cubic feet of interior storage space COLOR: Black stainless steel.']

title: Whirlpool Self Cleaning, Hot and Cold, Stainless Bottom Load Water Cooler with LED Indicators
features: ["6th Sense Self Cleaning automatically technology uses unstable Oxygen to get rid of the stuff you don't want in your water. The LED indicator shows when the Self-Cleaning is running, as well as when the cold and hot water are at optimum temperature.", 'Outlasts other brands as the compressor turns on less frequently because of the proprietary cooling system technology. The robust commercial design has unbreakable water faucets, a solid steel frame that can take over 300 lbs of top weight, and cold rolled steel sides']
description: ["*** IMPORTANT: The warranty is only valid if purchased from the authorized seller Reil Machines. Warranty service will not be provided for product purchased from other sellers.*** Self Cleaning technology uses automatic injections of unstable oxygen to get rid of the stuff you don't want in your water. The LED display shows when the self cleaning is running, as well as when the cold and hot are ideal temperatures. Enter your room on an angle, and the full stainless steel front is visible because of the curved front. This attractive showpiece is built to commercial grade standards, reliably producing very cold and very hot water. It's built to endure many years of heavy use. The most important feature of a water cooler is how well it cools, as many brands struggle to maintain 50°F, which is not cold enough. Whirlpool water coolers use a different type of cooling technology that forms ice inside the water tank, delivering refreshingly cold 40°F when you need it most, like during a summer heat wave. Likewise the hot water uses patented technology to maintain water at a steaming temperature, which guarantees a well brewed cup of tea. 5th generation bottom loading technology leaves less water behind in the bottle than other brands, and uses a heavy duty, commercial water pump that sucks the water powerfully with little effort. As the water pump is working at a fraction of its potential capacity, the motor is not stressed, and lasts for years of heavy commercial use. The commercial grade engineering features a compressor and thermostat that outlasts others by cycling a fraction of the time others do. The sturdy solid steel frame is built to take hundreds of pounds of top pressure. The faucets are engineered to be unbreakable with normal use, unlike many others that break off easily. The hot button is toddler resistant."]

description: ["Keep your drinks right where you want them, within arm's reach! It's time to stop running back and forth to the kitchen for refreshments when you can have them in every room of the house. This unit, one of Haier’s full line of beverage centers, holds 96 (12oz) cans or 46 bottles of wine. These drinks are held securely in place on six full-width black vinyl-coated wire shelves. You can choose the precise level of cooling with an adjustable thermostat, while the automatic defrost feature makes it virtually maintenance free. Think about that comfortable hangout spot in your house the place where people congregate, chat, and relax. Wouldn't it be nice to have cold drinks on hand and nearby for those get-togethers? Keeping this Haier beverage center in the den or game room could be the ticket for turning a nice place to relax into the ultimate hangout. Wouldn’t it be nice to have refreshments right there with you whenever you take a breather? Keep cool and hydrated by storing sports drinks and other refreshments nearby so you can get a better workout. What about the home bar? Rather than leaving wine bottles on countertops or stashed into the home refrigerator, a beverage center is the perfect piece to complete a classy home bar. Wine and beer will be chilled and ready, right where you need it. Let’s not forget about the kitchen! Get the clutter out of your main refrigerator by removing scattered soda and juice cans, and beer and wine. Keep them organized and handy in this beverage center, and make room in the family refrigerator for your home cooking. A Haier beverage center adds a sophisticated touch to any room."]

description: ["The Avanti can beverage cooler lets you store your favorite canned drinks at the perfect temperature with its adjustable temperature settings. Compact and stylish, this sleek black and stainless-steel beverage cooler is great for the home, office or small spaces like RVs and boats, or for supplementary drink storage in your kitchen. With 5.1 cubic feet of space, this beverage center can hold a total of 126 12 oz cans of your favorite beer or soda. You'll keep everyone happy by having plenty of their favorites chilled to perfection! This portable mini fridge boasts a durable and reversible double paned tempered glass door, which can easily be opened and closed on the side of your choosing and is the perfect mini fridge for the office, dorm, man cave, she shed, bar, bedroom, or anywhere you need a little extra refrigerator cooling and storage space. Easily see all your drinks through the glass door and use the adjustable, removable shelving for easy access to your favorite drinks. This compact fridge features automatic defrost, so your drinks stay consistently and perfectly chilled. Select the right setting at the touch of a button and monitor the temperature seamlessly with the LED electronic display. Designed for freestanding or built-in installation. Proper ventilation is required to maintain optimal cooling and overall performance. See instruction manual for proper installation."]

title: Summit Beverage Cooler, Grey/Clear
features: ['Make the best use of space by installing your refrigerator under the counter', 'Approved for use in the outdoors, with a sealed exterior and double pane tempered glass door', 'Heat resistant design provides clear view of stored products, with an elegant trim in seamless stainless steel', 'Ideal for home wet bars, island kitchens, and other applications with limited footprint space', 'Three glass shelves with six positions for optimal storage and easy cleaning']
description: ['The SPR489OS features a versatile design that meets NSF-7 and UL-471 commercial standards, but is also approved for residential use. Sized at just 19 inches wide and 17 inches deep, it features a jet black cabinet with a sealed back for safe installation in the outdoors. The user-reversible double pane tempered glass door includes a seamless stainless steel trim and a pro style handle. A factory installed lock offers added security, while the space-saving right angle plug and integrated hinge provide added flexibility in unit placement. Two leveling legs keep the unit level on uneven surfaces. Inside, the SPR489OS utilizes an internal fan to ensure the interior is evenly cooled from top to bottom. An automatic defrost system allows for minimal user maintenance, while the white interior and LED lighting allows full visibility of stored items. Three adjustable glass shelves with six positions provide optimal storage capacity inside the 3.1 cu. ft. interior. The dial thermostat, with seven temperature settings, is located in the upper-right corner for easy temperature management.']

title: SWBV3001 30 Dual Temperature French Door Beverage Center with 5.8 cu. ft. Capacity 35 Wine Bottle Capacity 3 Glass Shelves 6 Wine Racks and Automatic Defrost in Stainless Steel
features: ['Unique dual zone design lets you store wine and colder beverages under different temperatures', 'Flexible design allows built-in or freestanding use in 30" wide spaces', 'Stainless steel trimmed glass doors feature modern French door swing', 'Digital controls offer easy and intuitive temperature management', 'Factory installed locks offer added security to both sections']
description: ['SUMMIT\'s collection of built-in undercounter wine and beverage centers offers versatile choices for elegant storage in the home. The SWBV3001 is a 30" wide combination wine and beverage cooler designed for built-in installation under counters. It features a unique French door swing and two separate compartments with their own digital thermostat. The left zone is ideal for storing up to 35 standard 750ml bottles of red or white wine between 41º and 65ºF, while the right side operates between 40º and 50ºF to keep sealed beverages properly chilled. The wine compartment features full extension wooden shelves while the beverage side includes a mix of spill-proof glass shelves and a wire basket to accommodate a variety of items. Recessed LED lighting offers an elegant and efficient view of the interior. Both compartments feature their own factory installed lock. The glass doors come with a stunning seamless trim in stainless steel, with professional handles to complete the look. This unit has a jet black cabinet and stainless steel kickplate. Feature: Built-in capable Make the best use of space by installing this unit under the counter and flush with other cabinetry Dual zone design Two distinct temperature zones let you store wine between 41º and 65ºF and other beverages between 40º and 50ºF Seamless stainless steel trimmed door frame Single-piece door trim offers a more deluxe look Glass doors French door swing offers a modern look']

title: Avanti 9.5 Cu. Ft. Commercial Convertible Freezer Refrigerator Beverage Cooler with Sliding Glass Top, 2 Storage Baskets and Adjustable Temperature
features: ['Commercial chest freezer perfect for displaying ice cream, frozen dinners, and more in restaurants, convenience stores, or outdoor markets', 'Converts from a freezer to a refrigerator for use as a beverage or other foods cooler; Dimensions (L x W x H): 27.50 x 41.00 x 36.50 inches', 'Includes 2 removable storage baskets for a nice organized separation of items; Key security lock keeps merchandise or other belongings safe', 'Easy open sliding glass top display doors with handles for easy access to contents; Features adjustable temperature control and fast freeze setting', 'Easy-move rollers and defrost drain included for additional convenience; Power: 110V / 60Hz; Color: White/gray; Weight: 110.00 pounds']
description: ["For a freezer that can adapt to your needs, offering a lot of options for food and beverage storage, the Avanti Commercial Convertible Freezer Refrigerator Beverage Cooler is a perfect choice. With 9.5 cubic feet of space, this freezer works great for storing food like ice cream, frozen dinners, or hamburger meat for long periods of time. Completely convertible, it can also be used as a refrigerator to chill beverages or keep other groceries cool. The inside has 2 storage baskets for organization, but they can also be removed for extra space. The easy-open sliding lid with handles also has a glass window, so it's easy to see what you have left in stock. That lid can also be locked with an included key for security. Use the adjustable control and fast freeze settings to set the temperature according to your needs. This cooler also includes rollers for easy transportation and a defrost drain for additional convenience. Great for commercial and home use in restaurants, convenience stores, or garages, the Avanti Commercial Convertible Freezer Cooler is the perfect choice for those wanting a straightforward yet versatile way to store their food and drinks."]
